		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="Triggers by the first Gondian hostage to come out of the submersible after the rescue, if the players fought the Waveservants in the basement.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;All hostages are in the speaker group, so this should cover both male and female, and human, gnome and halfling races." />
